<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Experience Certificate</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 12pt;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .company-name {
            font-size: 20pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .company-address {
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .document-title {
            font-size: 18pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: underline;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            padding: 15px;
        }
        .certificate-number {
            text-align: right;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .employee-details {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px solid #000;
        }
        .details-table th,
        .details-table td {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        .details-table th {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .performance-section {
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .performance-title {
            font-size: 12pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 60px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }
        .signature-box {
            text-align: center;
            width: 45%;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding-top: 8px;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        .company-seal {
            text-align: left;
            width: 45%;
        }
        .seal-box {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            height: 80px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #666;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .verification-note {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
        <div class="company-address">{{companyAddress}}</div>
        {{#if companyPhone}}<div>Phone: {{companyPhone}} {{#if companyEmail}}| Email: {{companyEmail}}{{/if}}</div>{{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="document-title">Experience Certificate</div>

    <div class="certificate-number">
        <strong>Certificate No:</strong> {{#if certificateNumber}}{{certificateNumber}}{{else}}EXP/{{currentYear}}/{{employeeId}}{{/if}}<br>
        <strong>Date:</strong> {{currentDate}}
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p><strong>TO WHOM IT MAY CONCERN</strong></p>

        <p>This is to certify that <strong>{{employeeName}}</strong> was employed with {{companyName}} in the following capacity:</p>

        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <th>Employee Name</th>
                <td>{{employeeName}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Position Held</th>
                <td>{{position}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Department</th>
                <td>{{department}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{#if employeeId}}
            <tr>
                <th>Employee ID</th>
                <td>{{employeeId}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/if}}
            <tr>
                <th>Date of Joining</th>
                <td>{{joiningDate}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Date of Relieving</th>
                <td>{{relievingDate}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Total Experience</th>
                <td>{{#if totalExperience}}{{totalExperience}}{{else}}As per employment period{{/if}}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="performance-section">
            <div class="performance-title">Work Performance & Conduct</div>
            <p>During the tenure of employment, {{employeeName}} demonstrated exceptional professionalism, dedication, and competence in their assigned responsibilities. {{#if workDescription}}{{workDescription}}{{else}}The employee consistently met performance objectives and maintained high standards of work quality.{{/if}}</p>
            
            <p><strong>Key Achievements:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Consistently exceeded performance targets and objectives</li>
                <li>Demonstrated strong leadership and collaborative skills</li>
                <li>Contributed significantly to departmental and organizational goals</li>
                <li>Maintained excellent professional conduct and work ethics</li>
                {{#if achievements}}<li>{{achievements}}</li>{{/if}}
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>We found {{employeeName}} to be honest, hardworking, reliable, and a person of good character. {{#if gender}}{{#if (eq gender 'female')}}She{{else}}He{{/if}}{{else}}The employee{{/if}} maintained excellent relationships with colleagues, clients, and management throughout the employment period.</p>

        {{#if reasonForLeaving}}
        <p><strong>Reason for Leaving:</strong> {{reasonForLeaving}}</p>
        {{/if}}

        <p>We have no hesitation in recommending {{employeeName}} for future employment opportunities and wish {{#if gender}}{{#if (eq gender 'female')}}her{{else}}him{{/if}}{{else}}them{{/if}} success in all future endeavors.</p>

        <div class="verification-note">
            <strong>For Verification:</strong> This certificate can be verified by contacting our HR department at {{#if hrEmail}}{{hrEmail}}{{else}}hr@{{companyName}}.com{{/if}} or {{#if hrPhone}}{{hrPhone}}{{else}}+91-XXXXXXXXXX{{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="company-seal">
            <div><strong>Company Seal</strong></div>
            <div class="seal-box">
                [COMPANY SEAL]
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line">
                <strong>{{#if hrContactPerson}}{{hrContactPerson}}{{else}}HR Manager{{/if}}</strong><br>
                {{#if managerTitle}}{{managerTitle}}{{else}}Human Resources Manager{{/if}}<br>
                {{companyName}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> This is a computer-generated certificate and is valid without signature.</p>
        <p>{{companyName}} - Professional HR Document System</p>
        <p>Generated on {{currentDate}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>